        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/consumers/health-fraud-scams" title="Protect Yourself - Health Fraud Scams">Protect Yourself - Health Fraud Scams</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Buying medicines online, health fraud, warnings and enforcement, safety alerts, and reporting problems to FDA</p>
      </article>
     

       

       

       

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        
        
      
  </div>
