	<div class="lcds-cta__body">
		<h2 class="lcds-cta__title">
  <div class="field field--name-field-title field--type-string field--label-above">
    <div class="field--label">Call-To-Action Title</div>
              <div class="field--item">10 Facts about What FDA Does and Does Not Approve</div>
          </div>
</h2>
		<p class="lcds-cta__text">Is It Really &quot;FDA Approved&quot;? Maybe you’ve seen these words on a company’s website or in a commercial promoting a product or treatment. Here are some facts about products that are, and aren’t, FDA approved.</p>

    	    	<a href="/consumers/consumer-updates/10-facts-about-what-fda-does-and-does-not-approve" title="/consumers/consumer-updates/10-facts-about-what-fda-does-and-does-not-approve" class="btn btn-default">
