            <h3 class="lcds-card__title">Know Which Medication Is Right for Your Seasonal Allergies</h3>
            <p class="lcds-card__text">The pollen count is sky-high. You’re sneezing, your eyes are itching, and you feel miserable. Seasonal allergies are real diseases that can interfere with your life.</p>
